---
import Button from './Button.astro'
---

<section id="about-section">
	<div class="about-container">
		<div class="about-left-side">
			<div class="about-img-container">
				<img
					class="about-img"
					src="/images/dog-kisses_neo4lv.webp"
					alt="Woman kissing her golden retriever"
					width="420"
					height="300"
					decoding="async"
				/>
				<div class="yrs-exp-circle">
					<p class="yrs-text">
						<span class="about-bold-yrs">10 +</span>
						Years of Experience
					</p>
				</div>
				<img class="about-blob" src="./images/about-blob.svg" alt="blue blob shape" width="420" />
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="about-right-side">
			<h3>About Us</h3>
			<h2>We Are the Best For Your <span class="focus-font">Pet Care</span> Services</h2>
			<div class="header-underline"></div>
			<p class="about-text">
				At Epic Tales, we provide exceptional pet sitting services that ensure your pets are happy
				and comfortable while you're away. Our trained sitters are passionate about animals and
				committed to offering the best care possible.
			</p>
			<ul class="about-list">
				<li>
					<img
						src="icons/checkmark.svg"
						height="20px"
						width="20px"
						alt="checkmark"
						decoding="async"
					/>
					<p>Customized Sitting Plans: Tailored to your pet's needs and routines.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<img
						src="icons/checkmark.svg"
						height="20px"
						width="20px"
						alt="checkmark"
						decoding="async"
					/><p>Interactive Play: Engaging activities to keep pets entertained.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<img
						src="icons/checkmark.svg"
						height="20px"
						width="20px"
						alt="checkmark"
						decoding="async"
					/><p>
						<span class="bold-li">Regular Updates:</span> Photos and updates to give you peace of mind.
					</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="about-text">
				Whether it’s belly rubs, playtime in the yard, or sticking to their daily routines, we go
				the extra mile to make sure your pet feels safe, loved, and completely at home—even when
				you’re not.
			</p>
			<Button href="#" size="lg" style="secondary" class="about-btn">Read More</Button>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about-container {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1300px;
	}
	.about-left-side {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		max-width: 450px;
		height: 100%;
		width: 100%;
	}

	/* About Image Container */
	.about-img-container {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		z-index: 2;
	}
	.about-img {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: 3;
	}
	.about-blob {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		right: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		transform: scale(1.2) rotate(40deg);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	/* Years Exp Circle */
	.yrs-exp-circle {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 40px;
		left: -15px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--white);
		background-color: var(--primary-darkest);
		border-radius: 50%;
		border: 5px solid var(--white);
		width: 105px;
		height: 105px;
		z-index: 4;
	}
	.yrs-text {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}
	.about-bold-yrs {
		display: flex;
		white-space: nowrap;
		font-weight: 800;
		font-size: 1.3rem !important;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	/* About Right Container */
	.about-right-side {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: flex-start;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.about-right-side .header-underline {
		margin-left: 0;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.about-right-side p {
		padding-bottom: 10px;
	}

	.about-list {
		padding-bottom: 10px;
	}

	.about-list li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: start;
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 20px;
	}

	.about-list li p {
		padding: 5px 0;
	}
	.about-list li img {
		margin-right: 15px;
	}

	/* Small devices (sm) - 576px and above */
	@media (min-width: 576px) {
		.yrs-exp-circle {
			bottom: 50px;
			left: -15px;
			width: 130px;
			height: 130px;
		}

		.yrs-text {
			font-size: 1rem !important;
			font-weight: 600;
			line-height: 1.1;
		}
		.about-bold-yrs {
			display: flex;
			white-space: nowrap;
			font-weight: 800;
			font-size: 1.5rem !important;
			line-height: 1.1;
		}
	}

	/* Large devices (lg) - 992px and above */
	@media (min-width: 992px) {
		.about-container {
			flex-direction: row;
			gap: 4rem;
		}

		.about-left-side {
			flex: 1 1 50%;
		}
		.about-right-side {
			flex: 1 1 50%;
		}
		.about-img-container {
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}
	}
</style>
